glosses: to become fond of, develop a liking for

examples.translation: He became addicted to drinking and gambling.

examples.text: Düzce'de bal kovanlarına dadanan bir ayı, fazla bal yiyince kendinden geçti.
examples.translation: A bear that haunted honey hives in Düzce passed out after eating too much honey.

etymology: Cognate to Old Turkic [script needed] (tatġan-, “to enjoy, like the taste”), from [script needed] (tatıġ, “taste”). See tatmak.
